1 - Obtain note from Solomen in Temple of Solusek Ro<br>
2 - Give note to Camin in Erudin.  Hail him and give the 1000pp he requests.  (note - you must con warmly to Camin to get the response needed from the Hail, if you don't you'll need to raise Truespirit Faction - see below)<br>
3 - Purchase Ro's Breath from Dargon in Halas (about 1000pp)<br>
4 - Return to Camin in Erudin and give him potion and receive new potion.<br>
5 - Return to Halas and give potion to Dargon - she will turn into Arantir Karondor.  Get note/ring.<br>
6 - Give note/ring to Challise in basement of Felwithe Pally Guild.  Get new ring.<br>
7 - Back to Halas and give ring to Dargon, Arantir will spawn.  Get info on 3 wizards and get note for Kandin Firepot.<br>
<br>
KANDIN FIREPOT QUEST<br>
8- Hail Kandin Firepot in BBM receive gears<br>
9- Give gears to 'Broken Golem' in Plane of Fear - 'an Enraged Golem' will spawn..fight and obtain Green Oil.<br>
10 - Back to BBM and Kandin. Give Kandin the Green oil and receive Staff of Gabstik<br>
<br>
THE STAVES<br>
Collect 3 staves:<br>
10 - Staff of Gabstik (see 8, 9 and 10 above)<br>
11 - Blue Crystal Staff from Phinagel Atropos in Kedge Keep<br>
12 - Gnarled Staff from Ventril Sathir in Karnor's Castle<br>
<br>
ENDING<br>
13. Back to Dargon in Halas.  Give her note recieved in step #7 above to get Arantir to spawn.  Give him 3 Staff's.  Receive Pack<br>
14. Back to Solomen in Temple of Ro. Give him Pack get <br>
STAFF OF THE FOUR!!!!<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Truespirit faction -<br>
The easiest way I found to raise this faction is to the following - you'll need a chanter with the ability to charm...<br>
Go to BBM and kill Peg Leg, a lesser spirit will spawn.  Have your chanter friend charm it, then you hail the spirit and say &quot;I wish to know more&quot;..you will receive 'a tiny gem'.  <br>
You and chanter head to North Freeport to the tunnels and find *insert his name*. Give him the gem - but before you hit the 'give' button have the chanter invis you..he should now con indifferent to you.  Give him the Gem, and watch as your Truespirit Faction goes up.  You and chanter bind right here, port the two of you to PoK - head to Kaladim book.  Kill Mr. Leg once again...get the gem from the spirit and gate to North Freeport, and, well..you get the picture.  At some point the guy in Freeport will con indifferent to you, at which time the chanter can stay in BBM and keep the spirit entertained until you return.  Good Luck<br>
